OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780935073
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cin Birmingham
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a stabbing in Sparkbrook.
OL,9,FWest Midlands Police officers were
OL,10,Fcalled to reports of a stabbing in
OL,11,FWalford Road at around 6.20pm on
OL,12,FThursday, June 4.
OL,14,FA man had been stabbed and died a
OL,15,Fshort time later.
OL,17,FAhmad Alkozai, aged 29, from
OL,18,FBirmingham, was arrested in Bristol on
OL,19,FFriday, 5 June, and has been remanded
OL,20,Fin custody to appear at Walsall
OL,21,FMagistrates Court tomorrow.
