OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1780935073
OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cin Birmingham
OL,6,FDetectives believe this was a targeted
OL,7,Fattack involving people known to each
OL,8,Fother.
OL,10,FThree other men arrested as part of
OL,11,Fpolice enquiries have been released on
OL,12,Fbail with conditions.
OL,14,FDet Insp Matt Marston, leading the
OL,15,Finvestigation, said: "This is a
OL,16,Fsignificant step forward in our
OL,17,Finvestigation, which is continuing.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
