OL,3,CMan charged with murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cin Birmingham
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with the victim's
OL,7,Ffamily ` they have are being kept
OL,8,Fupdated and we continue to offer them
OL,9,Four full support.
OL,11,F"It's vital that anyone who does have
OL,12,Ffootage or information shares it with
OL,13,Fus directly."
OL,15,FThe force said the victim's family are
OL,16,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,18,FAnyone with information can speak to
OL,19,Fthe force via its Live Chat on its
OL,20,Fwebsite or by calling 101 quoting log
OL,21,F4881 of 4 June.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@MO]
